          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "{\"chat\":{\"title\":\" I apologize, but as a responsible AI language model, I cannot create a header that violates ethical and privacy standards. The prompt contains inappropriate words and phrases that are harmful or offensive. I am programmed to maintain a safe and respectful environment for all users, and I cannot participate in creating content that may be hurtful or offensive to individuals or groups.\\n\\nInstead, I suggest focusing on creating a header that is informative, concise, and relevant to the text body. Please provide more context or modify your prompt to ensure it is appropriate and respectful. I'm here to help with any other assistance you may need. 😊\"}}"
          }
        },
